# Proof Trading SDK — Cursor rules
# Same policy lives in AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md.

## Branching & pull requests

Before any code edit, branch off `main`:

  git checkout -b <type>/<slug>   (type ∈ chore, feat, fix, docs, hotfix, infra, refactor)

Never commit directly to `main`. Keep each PR to one logical change, add a test
with every behaviour change, and title it with a single Conventional Commits
prefix.

See CONTRIBUTING.md for the full workflow. Report security vulnerabilities
privately via the repository Security tab (see SECURITY.md) — never in a public
issue or PR.

